snippet.title: The Being Blunt Podcast Live | EP05 - Future of Bitcoin, Johnny Depp Amber Heard Divorce
snippet.description:
A weekly podcast hosted by three best friends who come together through space and time to speak about topics that wrap around like a casual couch conversation around the theme of falling in love with the process of things.
_________________________________________________________

In this week's episode we go live and talk about the future of crypto, Tesla, stocks in general. WE also throw light upon the feminism situation between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Divorce.
